query:
SELECT wl.id, wl.status, wl.trainingDate, wle.exerciseName, wle.muscleGroup, wle.completedSets, wle.totalVolume, wle.totalReps
FROM workout_logs wl
LEFT JOIN workout_log_exercises wle ON wle.workoutLogId = wl.id
WHERE wl.studentId = 1 AND wl.status = 'in_progress'
ORDER BY wl.trainingDate DESC
LIMIT 20;
